channel.title: Whitescape Release![DELTA] Summoning
channel.description:
Hello,first sorry for my bad English This is my first release,its from dds-specz Base - DELTA Features:
[ul][*]some 500+ emotes![/ul]
[ul][*]474 Prayer interface[/ul]
[ul][*]Animated 95% King black dragon![/ul]
[ul][*]5 Minigames(need to work on some because they dont work)[/ul]
[ul][*]Almost all skills working,they are better than Real delta[/ul]
[ul][*]Donator! With donator area and donator shop + Added crown!(donator area you can find in canifis)[/ul]
[ul][*]Owner crown[/ul]
[ul][*]5 Quests[/ul]
[ul][*]Summoning in delta![/ul]
[SIZE="5"]And alot more,i dont remember[/SIZE] [B][SIZE="6"]Some Pictures[/SIZE][/B] [B]King Black Dragon[/B] [IMG]http://img829.imageshack.us/img829/6445/00db68d53567772979bc140.png[/img] [B]HOME![/B] [IMG]http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/6153/4378220a7400d7d29b8305c.png[/img] [B]BARROWS[/B] [IMG]http://img197.imageshack.us/img197/994/aa7b4276688f8d7aa899a29.png[/img] [B]Dueal Arena[/B] [IMG]http://img651.imageshack.us/img651/5106/e27b68b2aa8c255c92d8a67.png[/img] [B]Skill Capes[/B] [IMG]http://img405.imageshack.us/img405/8272/unledzaw.jpg[/img] Proof summoning works! [IMG]http://img847.imageshack.us/img847/2652/unledirv.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://img824.imageshack.us/img824/4219/opam.jpg[/img] [size=18pt]If you need any help,my skype is paprastutis999[/size]
